title: Lost - 3x06 - I Do. XVID-XOR

I Do   

First aired: 11/8/2006    


Jack makes a decision regarding Ben\&#039;s offer; Kate feels helpless when it looks like Pickett is going to make good on his threat to kill Sawyer; Locke discovers a hidden message that may help unlock the island\&#039;s secrets.
